    • Method Detail

      • bindResultType

        Q bindResultType(String name,
                 Class<?>... resultTypes)
        Asserts the given resultTypes for the result denoted by name. This ensures that the result values for name have at least the resultTypes.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the result variable
        resultTypes - The types for the result variable
        Returns:
        The query object

      • restrictResultType

        Q restrictResultType(String name,
                     Class<?>... resultTypes)
        Restricts the types of the result values for name to the given resultTypes. This ensures that no additional queries are executed to retrieve the actual types of the result values for name.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the result variable
        resultTypes - The types for the result variable
        Returns:
        The query object

      • getFirstResult

        int getFirstResult()
        The position of the first result the query object was set to retrieve. Returns 0 if setFirstResult was not applied to the query object.

        position of first result

      • getMaxResults

        int getMaxResults()
        The maximum number of results the query object was set to retrieve. Returns Integer.MAX_VALUE if setMaxResults was not applied to the query object.

        maximum number of results
